{"tid":309371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友入左幾次都入唔到","createTime":"2017-07-05T03:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T03:54:37.000Z","uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a79e4bc1698edff439e07acc9d5d8e39eafad562","tid":309371,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"利申用緊男朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n試左幾次都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果喺出面磨下磨下磨下磨下<br />\n我心諗點解靜左嘅？<br />\n佢：我射左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：......<br />\n之後我話佢似望住我打飛機多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係我太窄入唔到<br />\n試過用手指，入左一節手指頭已經有啲痛，好似有野頂住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢見我痛就無繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點算呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584bb604cc211f10174d2dde694dfb79ff26ccff","tid":309371,"uid":30259,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"互射返兩次算啦"},{"pid":"1166dc8868d4a95ad9280d26a59a6c9efaa9b9cf","tid":309371,"uid":57741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"其實你係度問預左都係得堆標準答法"},{"pid":"25852eed4ea80a04dfaac4564b5cf03b2bd6ccd4","tid":309371,"uid":14241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"係咪你太耐冇痾屎"},{"pid":"06a170c6b26d0b97761586f52517613241ad105b","tid":309371,"uid":22202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"屎眼窄係正常嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296320f53430d7c2c681dd006599