.000Z","msg":"用ky"},{"pid":"ac716a4fc021631399f891bb5db8a59721e352e7","tid":309371,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"事前屙屙屎等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熱下身先"},{"pid":"b28d4723c2fa8c7570b325dee4a051402d98ea4f","tid":309371,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你男朋友係車頭大燈？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ba42ee2005f2a682ec60b9e6262770e5cb45e3","tid":309371,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你男朋友係車頭大燈？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇到topic都知係你"},{"pid":"d6a73dbe0310752deeeceab0bac55ff3ac95d560","tid":309371,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:16:45.000Z","msg":"無用牛油係難D"},{"pid":"2ea9a704c6e3082ff21a54c994bfed69720222f0","tid":309371,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:20:19.000Z","msg":"有啲人係會特別痛<br />\n試下由一隻手指，<br />\n慢慢加到幾隻手指先<br />\n（記得洗乾淨手先）<br />\n慢慢適應，叫佢入少少試下，唔好一野入<br />\n唔得就下次再試過，唔好格硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752c3320082b7cfce4325782bec5ce41ef1129de","tid":309371,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:27:51.000Z","msg":"你入到佢咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f960198498c82add72e6a2115024e0e250dcac31","tid":309371,"uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"你男友人品咁好，佢mind 你俾綠帽佢戴"}]}